__SqlaTable__.sql:
SELECT 
	-- Accident identification--
	c.Num_Acc
	,STR_TO_DATE(CONCAT(an,"-",mois,"-",jour," ",hrmn),'%Y-%m-%d %H:%i') as Date_Acc
	,CONCAT(WEEKDAY(CONCAT(an,"-",mois,"-",jour))," - ",DAYNAME(CONCAT(an,"-",mois,"-",jour))) as DayOfWeek
	,CAST(left(hrmn,2) as UNSIGNED) as Hour
	-- Location --
	,c.dep as departement
	,c.lat as latitude
	,c.long	as longitude
	-- Location Description --
	,fdagg.description as agglomeration
	,fdcatr.description as road_category
	,l.vma as max_speed
	-- Location Conditions --
	,fdsurf.description2 as surface
	-- accident conditions --
	,fdlum.description as light_condition
	,fdcol.description as collision_type
	-- user
	,(c.an - u.an_nais) as age
	,CASE WHEN (c.an - u.an_nais) < 14 THEN "0-14" WHEN (c.an - u.an_nais) < 18 THEN "14-18" ELSE ">18" END AS age_cat
	,fdcatu.description as role
	,fdgrav.description as gravity
	,fdsexe.description as sex
	-- vehicle
	,fdcatv.description2 as vehicle_cat
FROM 
	caracteristiques c 
	join lieux l on c.Num_Acc = l.Num_Acc 
	join usagers u on (c.Num_Acc = u.Num_Acc) 
	left join vehicules v on (u.Num_Acc = v.Num_Acc and u.num_veh = v.num_veh and u.catu <> 3)
	left join field_description fdagg on (c.agg = fdagg.value and fdagg.colname = 'agg')
	left join field_description fdlum on (c.lum = fdlum.value and fdlum.colname = 'lum')
	left join field_description fdcol on (c.col = fdcol.value and fdcol.colname = 'col')
	left join field_description fdcatr on (l.catr = fdcatr.value and fdcatr.colname = 'catr')
	left join field_description fdsurf on (l.surf = fdsurf.value and fdsurf.colname = 'surf')
	left join field_description fdcatu on (u.catu = fdcatu.value and fdcatu.colname = 'catu')
	left join field_description fdgrav on (u.grav = fdgrav.value and fdgrav.colname = 'grav')
	left join field_description fdsexe on (u.sexe = fdsexe.value and fdsexe.colname = 'sexe')
	left join field_description fdcatv on (v.catv = fdcatv.value and fdcatv.colname = 'catv')
